pageTitle: Itinerary for Saturday, May 6, 2017 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Saturday, May 6, 2017:

Montréal, Quebec

6:30 p.m. The Prime Minister and Ms. Grégoire Trudeau will attend the Fillactive Father Daughter Ball.

Closed to media.
